	(text "- Designed for any PD charger with 9V or higher profile\n- Use 5V addressable strips\n- must initially NVM program PD controllerto accept profiles >5V\n- RESET button to reset hardware\n- Entering flash mode: hold BOOT, press and release RESET, then\nrelease BOOT.\n- Entering run mode: press RESET (BOOT is already pulled high)"
